Restart IMM (IBM/Lenovo)
------------------------
0. Connect to the Web Gui
launch the restart IMM button
1. ssh root@<hostname>-sc
--> resetsp
2. if one cannot connect to the sp, then try asu tool from within the guest OS
sr <hostname>

/opt/ibm/toolscenter/asu/asu64 rebootimm --kcs
 OR
/opt/lenovo/toolscenter/asu/asu64 rebootimm --kcs

